<text><body>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0001a" n="0001a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a01"/><milestone unit="juan" n="1"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="1"/><cb:div><note n="0001001" resp="NCLRareBook" place="foot text" type="orig">國圖按：此卷子並非竺法護譯之「孟蘭盆經」原文，而為演繹該經之一種韻散來雜之講經文。其韻文每七字一句首釋經名意旨，云「願我慈親領受之，因茲息苦得停酸，免受倒懸三𢙣道，離𢙣鬼前休𢙣趣，得向<g ref="#CB29788"/>園礼世尊」。篇中每引一句經文，即加以講唱，並已有催唱經文之吟詞，如「大眾須生敬重心……經文次苐唱將来」，均合於俗講之儀式與體裁，惜祇演繹首數句經文，至「目連欲度父母報乳哺之恩」止。此卷子之抄寫年代從上述紙墨狀況，及唱文中有「自出分憂佐大唐」之語，或在晚唐時期。</note><lg xml:id="lgD03p0001a0101" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em"><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/><unclear/></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連依教便<note n="0001a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">脩【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0001a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">脩</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>行</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a02"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">供養三尊及大眾</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">福利遐超<unclear/>鬼趣</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">願我慈親領受之</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">因茲息苦得停酸</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">免受倒懸三𢙣道</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">離却鬼前休𢙣趣</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">得向<g ref="#CB29788"/>園礼世尊</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">因此厥号𥁄蘭盆</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">接引眾生交離苦</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不獨當初為目連</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">兼為今朝座下人</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">故知大聖不思議</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">流向𨶒浮化羣生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">為救世間諸苦難</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">名曰𥁄蘭清淨經</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">念觀世音菩<g ref="#CB16765"/><unclear/></l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a10"/><p xml:id="pD03p0001a1001"><note place="inline">仏子</note>。將釋此經大分三叚苐一序分苐二正宗
<lb ed="D" n="0001a11"/>苐三流通分三叚不同且初序分。<note place="inline">仏子</note>。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a12"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0001a1201" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">上来<unclear/><unclear/>即如斯</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">略与門徒分別<g ref="#CB22072"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">向下依經次苐陳</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不知道理復如何</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大眾<note n="0001a1401" resp="CBETA" type="add">須【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0001a1401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">須</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>生敬重心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><unclear/>道此經<unclear/>孝行</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0001a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">各各𣫍心合掌着</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">經文次苐唱將来</l></lg>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0002a" n="0002a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a01"/><p xml:id="pD03p0002a0101">經云聞如是一時。佛在舎衛國<g ref="#CB29788"/>樹
<lb ed="D" n="0002a02"/>給孤獨。</p><p xml:id="pD03p0002a0204" rend="inline"><note place="inline">仏子</note>。西方梵語名佛陁此
<lb ed="D" n="0002a03"/>土<g ref="#CB30244"/>為求斍者。自斍〃他覺<note n="0002a0301" resp="CBETA" type="add">行【CB】，他【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0301"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">行</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">他</rdg></app>圎滿。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a04"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0002a0401" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">覺行周圎号世尊</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">於中三覺不思議</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">別日与門徒廣分別</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">今且略明<g ref="#CB11180"/>妙法</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">願聞<unclear/>障<unclear/>消除</l></lg><p xml:id="pD03p0002a0608" rend="inline"><note place="inline">仏</note>言舎衛國<g ref="#CB29788"/>樹給孤
<lb ed="D" n="0002a07"/>獨園。<note place="inline">仏子</note>。舎衛國者好嘉名人物英雄心<note n="0002a0701" resp="CBETA" type="add">猛【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0701"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">猛</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>利。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a08"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0002a0801" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">国王太子兼長者</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">諸佛如来<note n="0002a0801" resp="CBETA" type="add">住【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0801"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">住</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>彼中</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">給孤長者湏達<note n="0002a0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">多【CB】，［－］【國圖】</note><app n="0002a0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">多</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">聞佛功徳心中喜</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">火急㱕来造精舎</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">便買<g ref="#CB29788"/>陁太子園</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">四十里地布黃金</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">建造如来說法<note n="0002a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">處【CB】，支【國圖】</note><app n="0002a1101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">處</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">支</rdg></app></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">殿宇樓臺徦日月</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">池<g ref="#CB08887"/>華菓用㽵嚴</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><unclear/>仏當日在彼中</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><g ref="#CB22072"/>這𥁄蘭清淨教</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">為救目連慈母罪</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">免交受苦<unclear/>生天</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">上来多叚義不同</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">𢝰<g ref="#CB22072"/>經文<note n="0002a1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，義【國圖】</note><app n="0002a1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">義</rdg></app>成就義</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a16"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">従此下反是別序</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連得道復如何</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0002a17"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大眾<unclear/>生敬重心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">六通之名當解釋</l>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0003a" n="0003a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">各各虔茶合掌着</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連得道唱將来</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a02"/><p xml:id="pD03p0003a0201">經云大目揵連始得六通。仏子。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a03"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0003a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">恰似世間慈母身</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">養得子時登官位</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">威勢人間皆𢝰怕</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">自出分憂佐大唐</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><note n="0003a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">忽【CB】，怱【國圖】</note><app n="0003a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">忽</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">怱</rdg></app>然憶着我耶孃</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">取向本州專侍奉</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">所得財物買珠瑱</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">將来奉獻我尊親</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">百味<g ref="#CB13251"/>羞皆給恭</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">日夜將心親侍奉</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">若也悶来交合曲</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">音聲歌儛不曾𠇲</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">朝〃甘脆父母前</l><l rend="text-indent:1em"><note n="0003a0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">晝【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0003a0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">晝</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>夜尋常居左右</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">所要之間皆<unclear/>有</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">意徒孝行遣人傳</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">今此目連亦復然</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">得道恰似為官位</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">憶得先亡念慈親</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">堕落三塗阿郍邊</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">遂將天眼更遙觀</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">欲覓尊親擬供養</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">直為亡来年嵗久</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不知神識落何方</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em"><note n="0003a1501" resp="CBETA" type="add">乃【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0003a1501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">乃</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>知證得六神通</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">根本還因求父母</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a16"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">羅漢六通為苐一</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">願報當初養育㤙</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0003a17"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">今此向下一唱經</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">欲度父母報㤙受</l>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0004a" n="0004a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">大眾好生合掌着</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">經文次<note n="0004a0101" resp="CBETA" type="add">第【CB】，弟【國圖】</note><app n="0004a0101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">第</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">弟</rdg></app>唱將来</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a02"/><p xml:id="pD03p0004a0201">經云目連欲度父母報乳脯之㤙。仏子。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a03"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0004a0301" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">自得既圎應合救物</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">懷其孝行欲報重㤙</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a04"/><p xml:id="pD03p0004a0401">經云度者即是度脫報㤙兩字通摽經
<lb ed="D" n="0004a05"/>題。且夫人生在世。父母為親。非母不生。
<lb ed="D" n="0004a06"/>非母不長。是以目連。報其㤙徳。仏子。</p>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a07"/><lg xml:id="lgD03p0004a0701" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">目連自得既周圎</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">理合救其親父母</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">心裏為懷行孝行</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">報<g ref="#CB31016"/>従来養育㤙</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">人生在世合如斯</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">父母深㤙湏報荅</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">想得當初養育我</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">受苦懷<unclear/>不可論</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">除其孝順在眼前</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">供給<note n="0004a1101" resp="CBETA" type="add">［－］【CB】，不【國圖】</note><app n="0004a1101"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">不</rdg></app>所湏不闕少</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">假使砕身千万刼</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不能報得母深㤙</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">將知㤙徳大難酬</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">我佛如来再三<g ref="#CB22072"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">奉勸座下佛弟子</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">大湏孝順莫因循</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0004a15"/><p xml:id="pD03p0004a1501">仏子。故父母㤙重經云。父母有十種㤙卆
<lb ed="D" n="0004a16"/>難報荅。</p><list><item xml:id="itemD03p0004a1604">一者懷胎守護㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0004a1611">二者臨產
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0005a" n="0005a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a01"/>受苦㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0104">三者生子妄憂㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0111">四者𠰸苦
<lb ed="D" n="0005a02"/>吐甘㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0204">五者迴乾就濕㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0211">六者乳
<lb ed="D" n="0005a03"/>脯養育㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0305">七者洗濯不淨㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0312">八者為
<lb ed="D" n="0005a04"/>造𢙣業㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0405">九者遠行憶念㤙</item><item xml:id="itemD03p0005a0412">十者究
<lb ed="D" n="0005a05"/>竟憐愍㤙</item></list><p xml:id="pD03p0005a0505" rend="inline">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0005a0507" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">適来雖<note n="0005a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">列【CB】，烈【國圖】</note><app n="0005a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">列</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】">烈</rdg></app>十㤙名</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a06"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">義理差殊都未解</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">門徒若要細分別</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">先生敬重後依行</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">苐一懷擔守護㤙</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a08"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">十月胎中常負重</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">慈母將心憂姟子</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">𢙢怕胎中不得安</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">生時受苦命如斯</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">赤血滂沲魂魄散</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">時向之間<g ref="#CB30220"/>却命</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">由怕姟兒有<g ref="#CB02167"/>殤</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">生了心中便喜歡</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">忘却憂愁如快樂</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">眷属親情皆𢝰喜</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">慶賀今朝母子安</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">漸〃姟兒長大時</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">乾處唯留與子眠</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">濕處迴將母自臥</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0005a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">洗濯之時無懈惓</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">乳脯養育不辝勞</l>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0006a" n="0006a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a01"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">寒熱都来為<unclear/><unclear/></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">怜念由如掌上珠</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a02"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">年登十五母由憂</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">𢙢怕造諸不善業</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a03"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">走去心中常憶念</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">仏前發願早㱕来</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a04"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">四時八莭不前頭</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不覺<note n="0006a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">目【CB】，［－］【國圖】</note><app n="0006a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">目</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>中雙淚下</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a05"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">時向之間不得見</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">恛惶惆悵似湯𤋎</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a06"/><p xml:id="pD03p0006a0601">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0006a0603" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">他家孝順由憂耶孃</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不孝之男廣造<note place="inline">𢙣業</note></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a07"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">他州外鄉逐樂不㱕</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">父母此間肝膓寸断</l></lg>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a08"/><p xml:id="pD03p0006a0801">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0006a0803" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">他家若是孝順之兒</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">解向家中親侍奉</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a09"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">若是心中不孝順</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">逃走他鄉𢝰不<note n="0006a0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">㱕【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0006a0901"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">㱕</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a10"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">囙脩向外嵗年間</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">逐樂何曾憶父母</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a11"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">所得錢財別受用</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">肯解將来獻二親</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a12"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">將知世界𨒫眾生</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">罪過愚膚不可<g ref="#CB22072"/></l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a13"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">不報其㤙不孝順</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">堕向三塗𢙣道中</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a14"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">奉勸門徒諸信心</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">莫作如斯不孝人</l>
<lb ed="D" n="0006a15"/><l rend="text-indent:1em">斈取目連心裏<unclear/></l><l rend="text-indent:1em">命終必㝎見慈尊</l></lg>
<pb ed="D" xml:id="D03.8701.0007a" n="0007a"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0007a01"/><p xml:id="pD03p0007a0101">仏子。</p><lg xml:id="lgD03p0007a0103" type="abnormal"><l rend="text-indent:1em">上来道理轉殷勤</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">聞道還湏行
<lb ed="D" n="0007a02"/>孝行</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">不但自家心裏了</l><l rend="text-indent:1em">也令眾罪
<lb ed="D" n="0007a03"/>速消除</l></lg><p xml:id="pD03p0007a0304" rend="inline">𥁄蘭盆經<g ref="#CB09083"/>
<lb ed="D" n="0007a04"/>觀。故題。此經讚<unclear/>不思冝留傳天下
<lb ed="D" n="0007a05"/>眾人知有緣得遇<note n="0007a0501" resp="CBETA" type="add">者【CB】，<unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0007a0501"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">者</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/></rdg></app>蓮花<note n="0007a0502" resp="CBETA" type="add">會裏【CB】，<unclear/><unclear/>【國圖】</note><app n="0007a0502"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">會裏</lem><rdg wit="【國圖】"><unclear/><unclear/></rdg></app>与君𠋣。</p></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>